textBeforeTable: Current Members The Alumni Advisory Board will provide support to Saunders College of Business through enhancing alumni networks, increasing alumni participation with the College, and the building of relationships between alumni and current students. Mission Founded in the 1980s as the College of Business Alumni Association, Saunders College of Business Alumni Advisory Board partners with the College on a number of alumni-focused initiatives. It has a special focus on increasing alumni engagement, giving, events (social and educational), and raising brand awareness.
